### 3. 更新資料傳遞

#### [MODIFY] [MainForm.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs)

在 [BuildPathVisualizationData()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#1036-1109) 中呼叫新的優先級 API：

```csharp
// 取得路徑節點優先級
var nodePriorities = _pathPlanningManager?.GetNodePriorities();
if (nodePriorities != null)
{
    pathData.WaypointPaths = nodePriorities
        .Select(n => new WaypointWithPriority {
            Position = n.Position,
            Priority = n.Priority,
            IsBlacklisted = n.IsBlacklisted,
            IsCurrentTarget = n.IsCurrentTarget
        }).ToList();
}
```

